%p Dear #{@user.first_name},
%p You have received a #{@appointment.is_video? ? 'video' : 'walk in'} counseling appointment from #{@appointment.mentee.full_name(false, @appointment.created_at)} on the #{link_to 'LoveRealm', root_url} platform.
%p 
  %strong Scheduled for: 
  %span #{I18n.l @appointment.schedule_for, format: :long}
- unless @appointment.is_video?
  %p  
    %strong Location: 
    %span #{@appointment.location}
    %br
    = (link_to 'See Map', "https://www.google.com/maps/place/#{@appointment.latitude}+#{@appointment.longitude}/@#{@appointment.latitude},#{@appointment.longitude},17z") if @appointment.latitude

%p Please login to your #{link_to 'LoveRealm dashboard', dashboard_appointments_url(kind: 'upcoming')} to accept, reject or re-schedule this request.
%p Kind Regards,
%p The #{link_to 'LoveRealm', root_url} team